dct_title_s: Geologic map of the Patterson quadrangle, Stanislaus County, California
dct_description_sm: by Thomas W. Dibblee, Jr.; edited by John A. Minch.
Relief shown by contours and spot heights.
"Topographic base map from available USGS 7.5-minute quadrangle Patterson CA 1953, photorevised 1971, photoinspected 1978. DMA 1758 I NW, series V895."
Includes quadrangle location map, index to adjacent 7.5 minute quadrangles, and index to sources of geology, most recent 1974.
Includes "pertinent references", most recent published in 1970.
